OL,3,CMan arrested in Craigavon on suspicion
OL,4,Cof Lisa Dorrian's murder
OL,6,FPolice believe she was murdered on the
OL,7,Fnight of February 27 or in the early
OL,8,Fhours of the following morning.
OL,10,FA 48-year-old man was arrested in the
OL,11,FCraigavon area on Thursday morning.
OL,13,FHe was arrested on suspicion of
OL,14,Fmurder, assisting offenders and
OL,15,Fpreventing a lawful and decent burial.
OL,17,FDetective Chief inspector Kerrie
OL,18,FForeman said: "Twenty-one years ago a
OL,19,Floving family were robbed of their
OL,20,Fdaughter and sister.
OL,26,@zD@OOU
