PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772741480
OL,3,CMan arrested in Craigavon on suspicion
OL,4,Cof Lisa Dorrian's murder
OL,6,F"Lisa, who was from Bangor, was last
OL,7,Fseen alive on the night of Sunday 27
OL,8,FFebruary 2005 in Ballyhalbert. It's
OL,9,Fbelieved she was murdered that night
OL,10,For in the early hours of the following
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,F"Our investigation is ongoing and we
OL,14,Fremain determined to provide answers,
OL,15,Fclosure and justice."
OL,17,FLast week a 40-year-old woman was
OL,18,Farrested in Bangor and a 42-year-old
OL,19,Fman was arrested in Scotland.
