OL,3,CMan arrested in Craigavon on suspicion
OL,4,Cof Lisa Dorrian's murder
OL,6,FThey were both arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder, assisting offenders,
OL,8,Fwithholding information and preventing
OL,9,Fa lawful and decent burial before
OL,10,Fbeing released on bail pending further
OL,11,Finquiries.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, a 40-year-old man was
OL,14,Farrested on Wednesday on suspicion of
OL,15,Fassisting offenders and withholding
OL,16,Finformation.
OL,18,FHe was later released on bail pending
OL,19,Ffurther enquiries.
